title: Was of the Roses: The Emergency Dump
description: Tiffany and her boyfriend Adam share their locations on their phones and Tiffany recently saw that her boyfriend Adam stopped at his ex girlfriend's house.  When she asked him about it he claimed it was to take an "emergency dump".  She's not buying it though...
